{"tid":1307122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"油塘「連儂牆」前爭執事件　一人准保釋另一人獲釋","createTime":"2019-07-11T12:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T14:36:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5487ffc4a99d3394eafc6a7af5704100fcc7562a","tid":1307122,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:09:05.000Z","msg":"油塘港鐵站對開昨晚有大批市民聚集，持不同意見的市民疑因設置「連儂牆」問題爭執。警方說接獲5宗報案，包括4宗普通襲擊和1宗盜竊，全部是昨晚在油塘站外發生，兩名分別56和57歲的男子被捕。<br />\n<br />\n兩名被捕男子中，其中一人獲准保釋候查，本月下旬要向警方報到。至於另一人，由於事主表示不追究，被捕男子獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n報案的人士年齡介乎17至33歲，他們表示在油塘站外懷疑被人襲擊。"},{"pid":"bd21bf5747753af20b7b7166c3dbdc36d5e93a0c","tid":1307122,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:10:08.000Z","msg":"【任務欄】<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306215</a><br />\n任務眾多，請自行因應人數及背後目的考慮做邊D任 ；黃色為主線任務；紅色係Boss <br />\n7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjp1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=7267ca31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjp1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=b25f7130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n7.12 - 6.12一周月行動 - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156221199385785/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhklsd%2Fphotos%2Fa.101378395784%2F10156221199385785%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjp1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=3375bca5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156221199385785/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n7.13 - 全民中銀撳錢 - <a href=\"https://t.me/loveBOC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FloveBOC&d